ls.\n\n## Candidate Hardening (Auto-Generated) - Verification\n- The `bootstrap_identity()` invocation was found in `promptclaw/cli.py` within the `main()` function, ensuring identity creation on first boot for all CLI entry points.\n- Integration tests in `tests/test_pal_agent.py` exercise the verifier and confirm it correctly fails when artifacts are missing.\n"}}
